description: I am a laid back, easy guy to get along with. My family and close friends are very important to me. I currently have to wonderful boys, they currently stay with my ex. I am a 23 year old male. I currently have my own landscaping business, and I also do auto mechanics on vehicles on the side. I am looking for a young female between the ages of 19-28 who would be willing to be in a truthful, healthy relationship with me. In a relationship I believe honesty plays a huge factor in success down the long run. If you think your that kind of person feel free to reach out to me.
